title: Does Everyone Have a Podcast?
description:
Written by Zack Phillips
Starring: Lisa Kleinman, Kelly Hudson, Jonathan Marballi, Langan Kingsley, Avery Monsen, Dan Hodapp, Jon Bershad, Kristy Lopez-Bernal.

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, July 8, 2013.

Filmed by Tom Levin, Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
